uccess=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pne1665703118161.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pne1665703118161.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pne1665703118161.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pne1665703118161\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Automatic CLSID Handling\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether automatic CLSID handling is used. If <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">CLSID</span> property is not available, because you do not need to specify a CLID. If <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code>, enter the name of the COM CLSID in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">CLSID</span> field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pne1665703118161__section_y2b_rbz_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d946849e63\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pne1665703118161__ul_nmz_rbz_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pne1665703118161__li_d42716e1_d42717e1_d42718e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnm1665702714020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnm1665702714020.html\" title=\"A Signature Implementation is a Development Object that defines the technology used to implement a signature, such as Uniface, COM, SOAP and so on. A Signature can have multiple implementations. Each Signature Implementation captures the technology-specific properties of the Signature, Signature Operation, and Signature Parameters.\">Signature Implementation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/